Privacy Policy



Last updated: September 9th, 2023



This Privacy Policy is for the Everyday Motivation application by Mitoza.

We do not store or transmit your personal information, nor do we include any third-party advertising or analytics software.

By downloading, accessing, or using Everyday Motivation, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy, and our Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to this Privacy Policy or our Terms and Conditions, do not use Everyday Motivation.


Everyday Motivation does NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal information or information that uniquely identifies you.

Everyday Motivation uses RevenueCat to handle subscriptions and in-app purchases. RevenueCat helps us validate App Store receipts, manage subscription transactions, restore purchases, and synchronize purchase statuses across various devices associated with your Apple ID. RevenueCat provides us with data on when a user first used the app and with information about purchased subscriptions. Transactions are tracked using an anonymous app ID. RevenueCat does not have access to any personal information (Place of processing: US). For further details, please refer to RevenueCat's privacy policy at: https://www.revenuecat.com/privacy.

Everyday Motivation does not collect any other data.



This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. If we make changes, we will notify you by posting the revised Privacy Policy on this page and by announcing it in the Release Notes. The date this Privacy Policy was last revised is indicated at the top of the page. By continuing to use Everyday Motivation, you agree to any revised changes.






Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about the Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at mitoza62@gmail.com.

